Package: redstr
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Red team string obfuscation and transformation tool
 Red team string transformation library and CLI tool for offensive security
 operations, penetration testing, and evasion techniques.
 .
 A comprehensive Rust library providing 30+ string obfuscation and
 transformation functions for red team operations, blue team defense testing,
 and purple team collaboration. Perfect for security professionals building
 tools like Caido, Burp Suite extensions, phishing frameworks (EvilJinx), WAF
 bypass testing, XSS detection, SQL injection testing, and bot detection
 evasion.
 .
 Features:
  - Zero required dependencies (core library uses only Rust std)
  - 30+ transformation functions
  - Builder pattern API
  - Command-line interface included
  - Performance optimized
  - Security-focused design
